{
  "stem": "14687.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when we used to go to work, they used to look if you've got knives or-- or salt.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because the Italians, they-- they used to be-- they could walk, you see?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They used to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were in prison, but they were not like the Jewish people, you see?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they used to give to the girls salt or anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she had that thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said, who is this rapa?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From who is that thing?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So nobody answer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they see who is sleeping here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was Leah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Oh, she's going to catch her to put it in the soup, you know, the dishes for soup.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were big and boiling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was like barrels, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they want to put her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then she was crying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They wanted to put her in the soup?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the-- in the soup.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she was running, running, running.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the sister, she was crying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said, oh, [NON-ENGLISH], don't cry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In Spanish she said, [SPEAKING SPANISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we-- and then we left here ourselves what we used to hear for-- from her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, after they didn't catch her, she says she's sick.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She went to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the hospital, what she used to do, they used to put in them the [? thermometer. ?] And because she was all right, she was not sick, so-- so-- so she used to take the thermometer and she used to do with her hand to make herself sick, not to come out from there-- because in case they kill her.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So like this, she save herself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then after, we were together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to sing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we met another Italian Jewish girl from Livorno.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was an opera girl, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
